<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>EduUniverse - Learn Without Limits</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #f4f6fb;
      color: #333;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #3f51b5, #673ab7);
      color: white;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
    }

    nav {
      background: #2c2f5d;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 15px 0;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 10px 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #ffd700;
    }

    .hero {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      background: white;
    }

    .hero-text {
      flex: 1 1 500px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .hero-text h2 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      color: #3f51b5;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .hero-text p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      color: #555;
    }

    .hero-image {
      flex: 1 1 400px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .hero-image img {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .features {
      background: #eef0f8;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .features h2 {
      font-size: 2.2em;
      color: #673ab7;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .feature-boxes {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .feature-box {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 25px;
      width: 280px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .feature-box:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
    }

    .feature-box h3 {
      color: #3f51b5;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .video-section {
      background: white;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .video-section h2 {
      font-size: 2em;
      color: #3f51b5;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .video-container {
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 56.25%;
      height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .video-container iframe {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: 0;
    }

    .about {
      background: #fdfdfd;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about h2 {
      font-size: 2em;
      color: #3f51b5;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about p {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: #444;
      font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    .signup {
      background: #eef0f8;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .signup h2 {
      font-size: 2em;
      color: #673ab7;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .signup form {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .signup input[type="text"],
    .signup input[type="email"],
    .signup input[type="password"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1em;
    }

    .signup button {
      background: #3f51b5;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border: none;
      font-size: 1em;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .signup button:hover {
      background: #5c6bc0;
    }

    footer {
      background: #3f51b5;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .feature-boxes {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>EduUniverse</h1>
    <p>Expanding Minds. Exploring the Universe of Knowledge.</p>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">Courses</a>
    <a href="#">Library</a>
    <a href="#">About</a>
    <a href="#signup">Sign Up</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h2>Welcome to EduUniverse</h2>
      <p>At EduUniverse, we believe education is the passport to the future. We offer dynamic resources, powerful tools, and global access to learners of all ages. Start your journey of lifelong learning today.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571260899304-425eee4c7efc?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="Student Studying in Library" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2>Why Choose EduUniverse?</h2>
    <div class="feature-boxes">
      <div class="feature-box">
        <h3>üìö Extensive Library</h3>
        <p>Thousands of books, videos, and materials for every subject and skill level.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-box">
        <h3>üåê Global Access</h3>
        <p>Join a diverse learning community from around the world, anytime and anywhere.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-box">
        <h3>üë®‚Äçüè´ Top Educators</h3>
        <p>Learn from experts and university instructors with real-world experience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="video-section">
    <h2>üé• Watch Our Vision</h2>
    <div class="video-container">
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mbl8sHzNm4E" title="EduUniverse Vision Video" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About EduUniverse</h2>
    <p>
      EduUniverse is more than just an online education platform‚Äîit's a movement to empower students to reach their highest potential. 
      With a mission to provide high-quality learning experiences, EduUniverse connects learners with trusted educators, a digital library, and interactive tools to thrive in a fast-changing world.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="signup" id="signup">
    <h2>Join EduUniverse Now</h2>
    <form>
      <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" required />
      <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" required />
      <input type="password" placeholder="Create Password" required />
      <button type="submit">Sign Up</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 EduUniverse. All Rights Reserved. | Designed for dreamers & learners.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
